<div id="rules" style="display: none;">
<ol>
	<li>
	Absolutley do not post any material that involves a minor doing illegal (under 18) activites.
	This will not be tolerated resulting in a ban from the website!
	</li>
	<li>
	Do not post any material that voilates local or webserver location laws. Breaking the law is strictly prohibited
	</li>
	<li>
	No spamming, automated bots, flooding, or scraping is allowed
	</li>
	<li>
	Please mark categories as (Not suitable for work) NSFW that will contain explicit material.
	</li>
	<li>
	If categories that are not marked with NSFW contain any material that is NSFW the content will be deleted!
	</li>
	<li>
	Please have respect for the board, quality posts make a quality board. Quality posts and content will be rewarded. Users who do not have respect for the board, other users and quality content
	will be banned from the website. 
	</li>
</ol>
